sentences.english: Senegal says it will extradite Habre on Monday.
sentences.chinese: 塞內加爾表示將於星期一把哈佈雷引渡回乍得。

sentences.english: In the small town of Kayar, 60km from the capital, Dakar, fishing is what people know best.
sentences.chinese: 無論你走在塞內加爾，魚總是菜單上必不可少的食物。

sentences.english: Hadi from Senegal is a technical director of a factory.
sentences.chinese: 哈迪是來自塞內加爾的一家工廠的技術總監。

sentences.english: How was your day?. My was little cold over here in Dakar Senegal.
sentences.chinese: 今天怎麼樣？。我是這裏有點冷在塞內加爾的達喀爾。

sentences.english: Nikky: yes, but he is a foe to the Frenchmen .
sentences.chinese: 塞內加爾隊的教練肯定是法國人的夙敵了。

sentences.english: Senegal got the break when Clinton visited Goree Island.
sentences.chinese: 克林頓參觀戈雷島之後，塞內加爾迎來旅遊高峯。

sentences.english: Foy and Kobylinski travelled to Senegal in 2008 to research malaria.
sentences.chinese: 佛伊與科貝林斯基2008年到塞內加爾研究瘧疾。

sentences.english: Frank Vandenbroucke has died while on holiday in Senegal.
sentences.chinese: 弗蘭克範登布魯克已經死亡，而在塞內加爾度假。

sentences.english: Evra is a French international, but he is actually from Senegal.
sentences.chinese: 艾夫拉是法國人，但是他其實來自塞內加爾。

sentences.english: The Sow family are volunteers who work with the Senegalese Government.
sentences.chinese: Sow家庭是與塞內加爾政府合作的志願人員。

sentences.english: 1935 - The Senegalese Socialist Party holds its second congress.
sentences.chinese: 1935年，塞內加爾社會黨舉行第二次代表大會。

sentences.english: In Senegal, more than 111,000 hectares have been infested.
sentences.chinese: 在塞內加爾，11萬1千多公頃的耕地遭蝗蟲破壞。

sentences.english: Senegal has decided to tow the corpse-laden MS Joola to its own territorial waters.
sentences.chinese: 塞內加爾已經決定將裝滿屍體的乘船拖至其自己海域。

sentences.english: Mine a little hot over here in Dakar Senegal.
sentences.chinese: 在達喀爾塞內加爾的這裏稍微熱地挖掘。
